				We've been massively asking for this on boards.  Now it's time to get serious.   <br>  <br> Let's all WRITE them.  This will be MY letter <br>  <br> Verant, <br> You want a solution to the rpers screaming for a server.  Here's my solution. <br> 1. Stop splitting off already crowded servers for a minute and start a new server labeled RP server. <br> 2.  ONLY label it.  No need to police.  No need to change any programming, just LABEL it. <br> 3.  Roleplayers from  ALL the servers will flock to it.  Suddenly ALL the OLD servers see a reduction on population easing up the strain on ALL Servers.  This gives the ones who stay behind, the powergamers, more breathing room. <br> 4.  The roleplayers are happy.  The powergamers are happy.  Verant has to do nothing.  All they did was write a label on a server. <br>  <br> The address to send this to is EQmail@everquest.com <br>  <br> Flood them with letters.  Don't ask for the ridiculous.  Don't ask to change programming, no whinning or flaming.  Just a respectful letter will do.		

